Print a prose narrative of what you did in the window

Usage: mxr activity replay [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --since <SINCE>    [default: 1h]
      --limit <LIMIT>    [default: 200]
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
